 ''[[Jayam (2003 film)|Jayam]]''.<ref name=\"notes\"/>\n* \"Jimmy\" incorporates elements of \"Jimmy Jimmy Jimmy Aaja\" written by [[Bappi Lahiri]] from the film ''[[Disco Dancer]]''.<ref name=\"notes\"/>\n* \"Mango Pickle Down River\" is remixed from the original recording \"Down River\" by [[The Wilcannia Mob]].<ref name=\"notes\"/>\n* \"20 Dollar\" incorporates elements of \"[[Where Is My Mind?]]\" by the [[Pixies (band)|Pixies]].<ref name=\"notes\"/>\n* \"World Town\" incorporates elements of \"Hands Up, Thumbs Down\" written by Blaqstarr.<ref name=\"notes\"/>\n* \"Paper Planes\" incorporates elements of \"[[Straight to Hell (song)|Straight to Hell]]\" by [[The Clash]].<ref name=\"notes\"/>\n\n==Personnel==\nCredits adapted from the liner notes of the expanded edition of ''Kala''.<ref name=\"notes\">{{cite AV media notes |title=Kala |type=expanded edition liner notes |others=[[M.I.A. (rapper)|M.I.A.]] |publisher=[[XL Recordings]] |year=2008 |id=XLCD281X}}</ref>\n\n{{div col}}\n* M.I.A. \u2013 vocals {{small|(all tracks)}}, production {{small|(tracks 1\u20136, 8, 9, bonus disc tracks 2, 3)}}, additional vocal production {{small|(track 6)}}, artwork, photography\n* [[Afrikan Boy]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(track 5, bonus disc track 1)}}\n* [[Jim Beanz]] \u2013 vocal production {{small|(track 12)}}\n* [[Janette Beckman]] \u2013 photography\n* [[Blaqstarr]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 9, bonus disc track 5)}}, vocal production {{small|(bonus disc track 1)}}\n* Demacio \"Demo\" Castellon \u2013 engineering, mixing, programming {{small|(track 12)}}\n* [[Cavemen (songwriters)|Cavemen]] \u2013 vocal production {{small|(track 2)}}\n* Conductor \u2013 production {{small|(bonus disc track 6)}}\n* [[Diplo]] \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 5, 10, 11, bonus disc tracks 1, 2, 4)}}, additional vocal production {{small|(track 6)}}\n* DJ Ability \u2013 cuts {{small|(track 6)}}\n* Marty Green \u2013 assistant engineering {{small|(track 12)}}\n* Liz Johnson-Artur \u2013 photography\n* Michael Kamber \u2013 photography\n* Lil' John \u2013 production {{small|(bonus disc track 6)}}\n* Steve Loveridge \u2013 additional graphics\n* Larry \"Live\" Lyons \u2013 assistant engineering {{small|(track 12)}}\n* [[Morganics]] \u2013 production {{small|(track 6)}}\n* [[Carri Mundane]] \u2013 additional graphics\n* Riot \u2013 production {{small|(bonus disc track 6)}}\n* [[Rye Rye]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(bonus disc track 1)}}\n* [[Mark 'Spike' Stent|Spike Stent]] \u2013 mixing {{small|(tracks 3, 4)}}\n* [[Switch (house DJ)|Switch]] \u2013 production {{small|(tracks 1, 3\u20135, 7, 8, bonus disc track 3)}}, additional production {{small|(tracks 2, 10, 11, bonus disc tracks 1, 4)}}, mixing {{small|(track 11)}}\n* Ron Taylor \u2013 vocal [[Pro Tools]] editing {{small|(track 12)}}\n* [[Timbaland]] \u2013 all instruments, production, vocals {{small|(track 12)}}\n* [[The Wilcannia Mob]] \u2013 vocals {{small|(track 6)}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|Chart (2007)\n!scope=\"col\"|Peak<br>position\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[ARIA Charts|Australian Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=M.I.A.&titel=Kala&cat=a |title=M.I.A. \u2013 Kala |publisher=australian-charts.com. Hung Medien |accessdate=30 January 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203043752/http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=M.I.A.&titel=Kala&cat=a |archivedate= 3 February 2014}}</ref>\n|46\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[ARIA Charts|Australian Urban Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pandora.nla.gov.au/pan/23790/20071020-0000/issue912.pdf#page=17 |title=ARIA Urban Album Chart \u2013 Week Commencing 27th August 2007 |publisher=[[ARIA Charts]]. [[Pandora Archive]] |accessdate=30 January 2014}}</ref>\n|6\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[\u00d63 Austria Top 40|Austrian Albums Chart]]<ref>{