3 2007: Top 50 Albums |publisher=[[Irish Recorded Music Association]] |accessdate=15 October 2009}}</ref>\n|22\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[Oricon|Japanese Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"oricon\">{{cite web |url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/artist/364138/ranking/cd_album/ |script-title=ja:\uff2d\uff0e\uff29\uff0e\uff21\uff0e\u306e\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u58f2\u308a\u4e0a\u3052\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0 |trans-title=M.I.A. album sales ranking |language=Japanese |publisher=[[Oricon]] |accessdate=30 January 2014}}</ref>\n|23\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[VG-lista|Norwegian Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://norwegiancharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=M.I.A.&titel=Kala&cat=a |title=M.I.A. \u2013 Kala |publisher=norwegiancharts.com. Hung Medien |accessdate=30 January 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308043637/http://norwegiancharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=M.I.A.&titel=Kala&cat=a |archivedate= 8 March 2014}}</ref>\n|22\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[Sverigetopplistan|Swedish Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://swedishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=M.I.A.&titel=Kala&cat=a |title=M.I.A. \u2013 Kala |publisher=swedishcharts.com. Hung Medien |accessdate=30 January 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203030952/http://swedishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=M.I.A.&titel=Kala&cat=a |archivedate= 3 February 2014}}</ref>\n|18\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[Swiss Hitparade|Swiss Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://swisscharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=M.I.A.&titel=Kala&cat=a |title=M.I.A. \u2013 Kala |publisher=swisscharts.com. Hung Medien |accessdate=30 January 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211100328/http://swisscharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=M.I.A.&titel=Kala&cat=a |archivedate=11 December 2013}}</ref>\n|74\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|[[UK Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"ukchart\">{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/3/2007-09-01/ |title=2007 Top 40 Official Albums Chart UK A